column5: Took 3 days, but we are finally in our new digs. Smaller yard to look after, which means more fishing time. Also a roomier house for my granddaughter to grow into. I even get a dedicated fishing room.  Now to spend a week unpacking so I can get back to making tackle.
Good luck in your new home!

Good to hear Bruce……good to hear
All the best in your new home.
Congrats on the new house,let's hear some details of the new digs! Usually a new house means less fishing time for a while....

Congrats on the new house,let's hear some details of the new digs! Usually a new house means less fishing time for a while.... Larger house and much smaller yard. So I should have a little more fishing time. Even have me a room just for all my, and my grandkids, fishing swag and tackle making.
